title: Melenas Live on KEXP from Mexico is out now

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico City with Melenas performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded October 18, 2024.

Songs:
1986 00:38
Osa Polar 04:56
1000 Canciones 09:26
Bang 13:42

Laura Torre - Drums, Vocals
Oihana Herrera - Guitar, Keys, Vocals
Leire Zabala - Bass, Vocals
María del Amor Zubiaur - Keys, Vocals

Live on KEXP in Mexico City is a partnership with Vive Latino celebrating its 25th anniversary with the support of Indie Rocks! Magazine. Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico.

Host: Albina Cabrera
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Carlos Cruz

Recorded by Matt Ogaz & JC Vertti
Assistant Engineer: Sebastián Garrido
Mixed By Jon Roberts
Mastered by Matt Ogaz

Vive Latino Support:
Jordi Puig
Itzel Flores

https://melenas.bandcamp.com
http://kexp.org
